nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 191 is the 169th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the ninety-ninth issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on July 24, 2019.

Star Wars Insider's journey through the Skywalker saga reaches the climax of the original trilogy, as we examine Star Wars: Return of the Jedi! Take a sideways look at the Rebellion era through the lens of Nintendo's Super Star Wars video game trilogy, discover the bio-diversity of the galaxy, and check out the boldest Star Wars tattoos! Plus, the launch of Star Wars Insider's Skywalker Saga Survey-your chance to vote for your favorite heroes, villains, events, and more from Episodes I to IX.
